item.title: License Plate Extraction - YOLO v4, Vision API (GCP)
item.description: The objective is to extract the registration/license plate number from different vehicle images. The task is divided into two parts. First, detect the possible ROI(region of interest) - in this case, it is the license plate of vehicles. Second, extract the letters and numbers from the detected region.
